{
  "stem": "1581.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I want to mention that the reason I'm here was that we were three of us who stuck together through thick and thin and helped each other as much as we possibly could.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I can say without exaggeration, all three of us survived because of our bond that we had.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The two were Pavel Loiv, who then, after the war, went  to Australia, and unfortunately died two-- two years ago.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The third one was my dear friend Sammy Schmueli, who is now in a kibbutz in Israel, and I just yesterday received a lovely letter from him.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] One of our muselmen was Dr.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Solomon, the man who saved his boots.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he told me, when I go, be sure to get my shoes, because in my left heel is a piece of gold in the heel.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So if you get into a situation where you need to bribe somebody, you will have something.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the three of us had-- the-- the-- the reason I was chosen to wear the boots, because I had very small feet, and they fit me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The others had big feet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was wearing these shoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And much later, when things became very, very bad, and we were cut off from our outside world and our supplier-- which will-- I explain later-- we decided we have to open our heel.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What will we do with the gold?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We knew our way around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were people who we knew could be bribed, and there was particularly one guy in the Waffen SS.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Which, Waffen SS was not a real SS.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was kind of a army unit, only it was attached to the SS.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this guy was known to be open to bribes.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
